body_html:
Thanks @rmuss This let me run the final make (step 9) however I get a lot of warnings and then some errors at the end. Here is the terminal output.

The updated protobuf build steps are now :

  1. pi@raspberrypi:~/ $ sudo apt-get install autoconf automake libtool curl make g++ unzip
  2. pi@raspberrypi:~/ $ cd ~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf
  3. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo ./autogen.sh
  4. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo ./configure
  5. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo make
  6. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo make install
  7. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ cd ../../../../..
  8. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow $ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/lib
  9. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow $ make -f tensorflow/contrib/makefile/Makefile HOST_OS=PI TARGET=PI OPTFLAGS="-Os -mfpu=neon-vfpv4 -funsafe-math-optimizations -ftree-vectorize"

body:
Thanks @rmuss This let me run the final make (step 9) however I get a lot of warnings and then some errors at the end. [Here is the terminal output](https://drive.google.com/open?id=0B0Oci8Q1NdEuSWRrXzV4czVPQ3pCaUktSl8xR2NNY19RWmU0). 

The updated protobuf build steps are now :
1. pi@raspberrypi:~/ $ sudo apt-get install autoconf automake libtool curl make g++ unzip
2. pi@raspberrypi:~/ $ cd ~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf
3. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo ./autogen.sh
4. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo ./configure
5. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo make
6. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ sudo make install
7. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow/tensorflow/contrib/makefile/downloads/protobuf $ cd ../../../../..
8. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow $ export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/lib
9. pi@raspberrypi:~/tensorflow $ make -f tensorflow/contrib/makefile/Makefile HOST_OS=PI TARGET=PI OPTFLAGS="-Os -mfpu=neon-vfpv4 -funsafe-math-optimizations -ftree-vectorize"
